<!DOCTYPE HTML>
<html>
<head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
    <link href="http://c.wedpl.com/favicon.ico" rel="shortcut icon" type="image/x-icon">
    <title>注册-结婚计划网</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/login_reset.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/login_style.css">
    <script src="/js/jQuery.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
    <script src="/js/script.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
</head>
<body>
<div class="login_head"><a href="http://www.wedpl.com"><img src="/images/logo.png"></a></div>
<div class="login_wrap">
    <div class="login_con">
        <div class="weixinbox"><span><img src="" alt=""></span></div>
        <div class="info_box">
            <div class="info_tit"><span><a href="/site/login.html">登录</a></span><span class="on"><a href="/site/signup.html">注册</a></span></div>
            <div class="info_con">
                <div class="reg_cont">
                    <form action="/site/signup.html" method="post" id="sign_form">
			<p class="reg_name"><input type="text" id="reg_username" name="Signup[username]" placeholder="用户名"></p>
                        <p class="reg_name"><input type="text" id="reg_phone" name="Signup[phone]" placeholder="输入手机号"></p>
                        <p class="reg_password"><input type="password" id="reg_password"  name="Signup[password]" placeholder="密码"></p>                   
                        <p class="reg_password"><input type="password" id="reg_pwd" name="Signup[password]" placeholder="重复密码"></p>
			<p class="reg_message"><span class="warn_btn"></span><span class="reg_messagewarm"></span></p>
			<p class="reg_btn" id="sign_sub">立即注册</p>
                    </form>
                </div>
                <div class="yy-yzm" id="yy_unbind"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="login_foot">
	<a href="http://nb.wedpl.com/hunsha/">婚纱摄影</a> | <a href="http://nb.wedpl.com/ertong/">儿童摄影</a> | <a href="http://nb.wedpl.com/hunqing/">婚庆服务</a> | <a href="http://nb.wedpl.com/hunshalifu/">婚庆礼服</a> | <a href="http://nb.wedpl.com/jiudian/">婚庆酒店</a> | <a href="http://nb.wedpl.com/shoushi/">婚戒首饰</a>
